title: Chemtech Tryndamere not available?
body: Hey just wanted to know why chemtech tryndamere isn't available for purchase, i thought it was suppose to be come out this patch? I see it come out when i click on the champ and go to his skins, but i don't see it on the store.

replies.body: You're right, it is aimed to come out this patch!  The patch just came out though, and new content doesn't necessarily come out the day of.  Bookmark our [News](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/news/) page for news on our chemical war king.  Hang tight!
